Package: hfsplus-dkms-source
Architecture: all
Depends: module-assistant, debhelper (>= 7), make, bzip2
Description: source for the hfsplus-dkms driver.
 This package provides the source code for the hfsplus-dkms kernel modules.
 The hfsplus-dkms package is also required in order to make use of these
 modules. Kernel source or headers are required to compile these modules.
